description:
This video shows how to project any textures from Omni point lights, rectangular lights or spot lights in UE 5 as well as how to do light linking (lighting channels) and flipbook animations. I also gloss over using midjourney and dalle-2 artificial intelligence. (One for a future video maybe?)

0:00 Intro
00:56 Light function material
01:54 Light linking
04:18 Flipbook animations
05:26 Why? and using AI

Check out these creators that helped me to figure this out. 
Thosesixfaces - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZskAizpzRU
Ben Cloward - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjTjj-dVGCE 
Postcitizen - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KNR27uPhswE
UE docs on light functions - https://docs.unrealengine.com/4.27/en-US/BuildingWorlds/LightingAndShadows/LightFunctions/
